.DS_Store

# Python/runtime cleanup
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
venv/
uv.lock

# Local environment / credentials
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key

# Blind-review hygiene — NEVER commit private author notes into the review pack.
paper/authors.private.md
**/authors.private.md
**/*.private.md

# Paper-enhancer phase outputs are tracked scaffold artifacts for NEE-1254.
# Keep arbitrary local scratch out, but allow the committed phase markdown files.
paper/*

# Local/generated submission bundles are not part of the public source repo.
# Keep the public readiness checklist at the repository root instead.
submission/

# M5 deliverable: the headline figure rendered from baseline_vs_guarded.csv
# is tracked. Its renderer (eval/render_figure.py) is deterministic given
# the CSV input.
docs/*
!docs/figures/
docs/figures/*
!docs/figures/headline_ser.svg
!docs/figures/headline_ser.pdf
!docs/figures/README.md
